S.FORM: Roch Marc Christian Kaboré I 1957 a miheca saka 4 folad saka 25 a romi'ad masofoc ci Roch Marc Christian Kaboré, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Burkina faso anini i ci Roch Marc Christian Kaboré, patirengan a romi'ad i 2015 a miheca saka 12 folad saka 29 a romi'ad.
